cs.DB, cs.HC, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the quality of data in spreadsheets, which is closely related to database management (cs.DB) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). It also touches on issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE) in terms of ensuring the accuracy and reliability of data. Finally, the paper discusses the presentation of data, which could fall under the category of computational science (cs.CY).
